      "type": "html",
      "text": "<i>The PARC innovations didn't \"escape\" into the outside world, especially to Apple. Xerox was an <b>investor</b> in Apple, PARC technology was intentionally demonstrated to Steve Jobs with the explicit goal (on the part of Xerox) of stimulating his interest, and the result was consistent with the mission of PARC.</i>",
      "id": "06dac42c0b19e19da7c168bccd8557e6"
